summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 5E, page 43 of the official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property located on the west side of 15th Avenue N.E., beginning at a point 120 feet south of N.E. 80th Street and extending 160 feet south, from Single Family Residence High Density (RS 5000) Zone to Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone. (Petition of Paul Panagakis, et al., 289633).
